{
  "texts": [
    "I desire that they turn from evil and walk in righteousness.\"",
    "11 When Jonah heard this, he was humbled.",
    "He saw that the Lord is merciful and slow to anger, abounding in love.",
    "And Jonah rejoiced that the Lord had compassion on the city of Nineveh.",
    "10 Then Jonah stayed many days in Nineveh, teaching the people the ways of the Lord."
  ]
}